---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import LeadMagnetForm from '../components/LeadMagnetForm.jsx';
---

<Layout
  title="Get Found on Google - Free Setup Guide | YourHQ"
  description="A free step-by-step guide to setting up your Google Business Profile. No jargon. No homework. Just the steps. For NZ small businesses."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-bone min-h-screen font-sans text-carbon selection:bg-deepGreen selection:text-white">

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-40 md:pb-32 border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 text-center">

        <!-- Refined Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1.5 bg-white rounded-full border border-carbon/5 shadow-subtle mb-10">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-signal rounded-full"></span>
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-softGrey">Free Guide</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Tension Technique Heading -->
        <h1 class="font-display text-hero font-bold text-carbon mb-6">
          Get Found on Google<br />
          <span class="font-serif italic text-headline text-terracotta block mt-4">The No-Nonsense Setup Guide</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="font-sans text-subhead text-softGrey max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Half of NZ businesses still don't have a proper Google presence. Not because they don't want one - because every guide makes it sound harder than it is. <strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">This one's different.</strong>
        </p>

        <a href="#get-the-guide" class="inline-block bg-signal text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-carbon hover:shadow-float transition-all duration-300 mb-6">
            Get the Free Guide &rarr;
        </a>

        <p class="font-mono text-badge text-softGrey">Takes 20 minutes. You'll need your phone and a coffee. That's it.</p>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE PROBLEM (Dark Section) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-white text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
            <!-- Tension Technique on Dark -->
            <h2 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-bone mb-10">
              You're Invisible to New Customers.
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-subhead text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <p>When someone Googles "plumber near me" or "best café in [your town]" - do you show up?</p>
                <p class="font-medium text-bone">
                  If you don't have a Google Business Profile, the answer is <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta text-3xl">no</span>. And that's work walking straight to your competitor.
                </p>
                <div class="pt-10 mt-10 border-t border-white/10">
                    <p class="font-sans text-body text-white/60">
                      The good news? Setting it up is <span class="text-bone font-medium">free</span>, takes about <span class="text-bone font-medium">20 minutes</span>, and this guide walks you through every step.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHAT'S INSIDE -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-surface border-b border-carbon/10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">

                <!-- Left: The "Book" Visual (Elevated) -->
                <div class="relative max-w-sm mx-auto w-full">
                    <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-white rounded-xl border border-carbon/5 shadow-elegant p-10 flex flex-col justify-center text-center relative z-10">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-surface border border-carbon/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-8 mx-auto shadow-sm">
                          📍
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-display text-headline font-bold text-carbon leading-tight mb-4">
                          Get Found<br/>on <span class="font-serif italic text-signal">Google</span>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="font-mono text-badge text-softGrey mb-8">YourHQ Setup Guide</p>
                        <div class="inline-flex mx-auto border-t border-carbon/10 pt-6">
                            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-deepGreen">Free PDF</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right: The List -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-headline font-bold text-carbon mb-10">What you'll get:</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-6">
                        <li class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border border-carbon/10 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-carbon shadow-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</div>
                            <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey"><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Step-by-step setup instructions</strong> that actually make sense</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border border-carbon/10 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-carbon shadow-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</div>
                            <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey"><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Category recommendations</strong> for tradies, salons, and service businesses</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border border-carbon/10 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-carbon shadow-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</div>
                            <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey"><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Verification tips</strong> so you don't get stuck at the tricky part</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border border-carbon/10 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-carbon shadow-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</div>
                            <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey"><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">What to do once you're live</strong> - the maintenance is lighter than you think</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-5 items-start">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border border-carbon/10 flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xs text-carbon shadow-sm shrink-0 mt-0.5">5</div>
                            <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey"><strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">Photo and description tips</strong> that make your listing stand out</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHO THIS IS FOR -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-bone border-b border-carbon/10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-carbon/5 p-10 md:p-16 shadow-subtle">
                
                <h2 class="font-mono text-badge text-terracotta mb-10 text-center">This guide is for you if...</h2>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-6">
                    <p class="flex items-start gap-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey">
                        <span class="text-terracotta mt-1">-</span>
                        You don't show up when people Google your business name
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex items-start gap-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey">
                        <span class="text-terracotta mt-1">-</span>
                        You've been meaning to "do the Google thing" but haven't got round to it
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex items-start gap-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey">
                        <span class="text-terracotta mt-1">-</span>
                        You tried setting it up once and got stuck on verification
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex items-start gap-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey">
                        <span class="text-terracotta mt-1">-</span>
                        Your competitors show up on Google Maps and you don't
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex items-start gap-4 font-sans text-body text-softGrey md:col-span-2 md:max-w-lg md:mx-auto">
                        <span class="text-terracotta mt-1">-</span>
                        You want new customers to find you without relying 100% on word-of-mouth
                    </p>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FORM SECTION -->
    <section id="get-the-guide" class="py-24 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">

            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-carbon mb-4">
                  Get Your <span class="font-serif italic text-signal">Free</span> Copy
                </h2>
                <p class="font-sans text-subhead text-softGrey">Enter your details and the guide will open straight away.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Elevated Form Container -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-elegant border border-carbon/5">
                <LeadMagnetForm client:load source="google-guide" buttonText="Get The Guide" pdfUrl="/get-found-google-maps-tradie-guide.pdf" />
            </div>

            <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
            <div class="mt-20 text-center border-t border-carbon/10 pt-12">
                <p class="font-sans text-ui text-softGrey leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto">
                    This guide is brought to you by <strong class="text-carbon font-semibold">YourHQ</strong>. Hand-coded, permanently owned websites for established business owners and personal brands. One conversation. Looked after forever. Need more than just a Google listing? <a href="/" class="text-carbon font-medium underline decoration-carbon/20 underline-offset-4 hover:text-signal transition-colors">See what we do</a>.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>